{
  "stem": "17374.4",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I think that's wonderful, because I got my grandchildren.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Now we are not having the dinner, but we used to have, every Monday, dinner for 15 people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "My husband was the cook.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I was the help.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we set up the table, and we-- they have come together, and we have a lovely time, yeah.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I tell you what, when I see the news, what is happening, I am very bitter.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I thought that that war will be-- will be that lesson for the whole earth.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was thinking that finished.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "People don't-- wouldn't kill each other anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I-- I'm-- I'm terribly nervous, you see.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Since I came to Melbourne, since even before, I start to take the relaxing tablets.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I went-- come to Melbourne, I went to Dr.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE]-- Valium, or Librium, or Valium, or Librium, because I have bad dreams, and that bad dreams.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And even now, from time to time-- not long ago, I had a dream that German are pulling me by hair.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it's so many years.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But in the beginning, I didn't talk about this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I didn't want to talk.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And honestly, I thought that-- gone, it's finished.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That-- that it's finished, nobody will know about it, what we went through.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And it's all-- but somehow, it-- I don't know why.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It comes out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Some people want to talk [INAUDIBLE] that when Kenneally came to us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he was sitting here with Leo, talking, and I went to garden.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I said I didn't want to say anything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I make them a cup of tea, and again I went to-- but eventually, even before-- yes, after the Kenneally that was-- that was made by [INAUDIBLE] from television, that was documentary.",
      "word_count": 32
    }
  ],
